ATK: This stat increases with your average points won in the last 100 games;

DEF: This stat increases as your deal-in rate over the last 100 games decreases;

SPD: This stat increases as your win rate over the last 100 games increases;

LUK: This stat is higher when you had more Dora-Yaku (Dora, Ura Dora, Red Five & Ippatsu) in the last 20 wins.
